<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Friendship Day Message</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Pacifico&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4f8 0%, #e0e8f0 100%);
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #ff6f61;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .friend-gallery {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .friend-card {
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .friend-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .friend-card img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 4px solid #ff6f61;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .friend-card:hover img {
            border-color: #ff9a8d;
        }

        .message-container {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-left: 5px solid #ff6f61;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            display: none;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.9);
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .message-container.visible {
            display: block;
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        .message-container h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #ff6f61;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .message-container p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Happy Friendship Day!</h1>
        <p>
            Click on a photo to see a special message.
        </p>

        <div class="friend-gallery">
            <div class="friend-card" id="joy-card">
                <img src="https://placehold.co/150x150/ff9a8d/ffffff?text=Joy" alt="Joy">
                <h3>Joy</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="friend-card" id="christian-card">
                <img src="https://placehold.co/150x150/66aaff/ffffff?text=Christian" alt="Christian">
                <h3>Christian</h3>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="joy-message" class="message-container">
            <h3>To Joy,</h3>
            <p>
                To one of the most cheerful and caring people I know, happy Friendship Day! You always know how to brighten any room and make me feel like I can take on the world. Your support and kindness mean more to me than words can say, and I'm so grateful for all our shared laughs and memories. Here's to many more!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div id="christian-message" class="message-container">
            <h3>To Christian,</h3>
            <p>
                Happy Friendship Day to the best friend a person could ask for. Thank you for being a constant source of loyalty, honesty, and for always being there, no matter what. Your friendship has made such a positive impact on my life, and I truly value the time we've spent together. I'm looking forward to all the adventures yet to come!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const joyCard = document.getElementById('joy-card');
            const christianCard = document.getElementById('christian-card');
            const joyMessage = document.getElementById('joy-message');
            const christianMessage = document.getElementById('christian-message');

            function hideAllMessages() {
                joyMessage.classList.remove('visible');
                christianMessage.classList.remove('visible');
            }

            joyCard.addEventListener('click', function() {
                hideAllMessages();
                joyMessage.classList.add('visible');
            });

            christianCard.addEventListener('click', function() {
                hideAllMessages();
                christianMessage.classList.add('visible');
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
